    <abstract id="aspace_fb5375f9479f840b254aa141fdd6a706" label="Abstract">This collection contains the records of St. Peter's Episcopal Church, Pittsburgh (Oakland), Pa. It includes a historical sketch, parish registers, minutes of the Women's Guild, register of church services, deed to Burgwin pew, correspondence, newsclippings, and photographs.</abstract>
